97
00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:21.240
All right.

98
00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:23.860
So here's where the sculptor metaphor breaks down.

99
00:07:23.860 --> 00:07:29.980
So we won't be returning to it too much because a sculpture is very passive when it comes

100
00:07:29.980 --> 00:07:31.400
