Get to work by the power of the Spirit who is at work in you.

109
00:07:55.240 --> 00:08:01.440
Work out what God has worked in so that we are active participants in the process of

110
00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:04.600
our growth in Christ's likeness.

111
00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:07.320
So there's certain things we must learn to say no to and certain things we must

