117
00:08:23.600 --> 00:08:28.080
And so instead of just looking at the big picture of the sculpture, if you will, he

118
00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:32.000
then now takes us closer and he says, now here, look, this is what the mouth is to

119
00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.000
look like.

120
00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:36.560
If you look a bit closer at the hands, like this is what the hands should look

