00:08:37.560 --> 00:08:41.400
We list out several areas of life and we're going to look through those this morning.

123
00:08:41.400 --> 00:08:42.840
There's kind of bullet points that are here.

124
00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:45.040
You just, we're just going to go through the list together.

125
00:08:45.040 --> 00:08:48.480
But before we go through the list, just a couple of things to keep your eye out

126
00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:49.480
for.

127
00:08:49.480 --> 00:08:53.360
One of them is the fact that there's a negative and a corresponding positive right

128
00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:55.000
the way through in the list.

129
00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:58.360
So there's things to put off and things to put on.

130
00:08:58.360 --> 00:09:00.640
So holiness isn't just about saying no.

131
00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:03.320
It's also about saying yes.

132
00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:06.480
And also another thing with what we see in this list is that all of these things

