00:09:56.360 --> 00:10:01.920
The first thing we read being spoken of here in verse 25 is lying and truthfulness.

149
00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:03.840
So you see the negative and the positive.

150
00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:12.120
Therefore, having put away all falsehood, let each of you speak the truth with his neighbor,

151
00:10:12.120 --> 00:10:15.200
for we are members of one another.

152
00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:21.400
It's been said for years that a lie can travel halfway around the world while the truth

